There is very little industry in our block as can be readily seen from the map. { The Northern area}
To the North of The Eyes lies the {abattoir}belonging to Gaskells the area's local curers and supplier of bacon. In the same location can be found a number of small industrial concerns chief among which is a plastics factory. {The Southern area
To the South of the Manchester Ship Canal and just to the West of the old village of Thelwall lies a recently abandoned wire works. It is now being refurbished as a collection of small factories and warehouses although their exact use is not known.
